    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0407b20"/><lb ed="T" n="0407b20"/><persName key="A002347">釋法莊</persName>，姓申，<placeName key="PL000000016390">淮南</placeName>人。十歲出家，為<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬山</placeName><persName key="A001204">慧<lb ed="T" n="0407b21"/>遠</persName>弟子。少以苦節標名。晚遊<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>，從<persName key="A002225">叡<lb ed="T" n="0407b22"/>公</persName>稟學。<date key="j18816401883959" notAfter-iso="0446" notBefore-iso="0439-08">元嘉初</date>出<placeName key="PL000000008976">都</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000010767">道場寺</placeName>。性率素止<lb ed="T" n="0407b23"/>一中而已。誦《大涅槃》、《法華》、《淨名》。每後夜諷<lb ed="T" n="0407b24"/>誦，比房常聞<persName key="A002347">莊</persName><ptr target="fn18"/>戶前有如兵仗羽衛之響，<lb ed="T" n="0407b25"/>實天神來聽也。<date key="j18880181890941" notAfter-iso="0465" notBefore-iso="0457">宋大明</date>初卒於<placeName key="PL000000010767">寺</placeName>，春秋七十<lb ed="T" n="0407b26"/>有六。</p>
